            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SUPPLIES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>Research and development of a very-light-weight rail-guided people mover with integrated battery powered propulsion; and of a low-cost, easy to install track solution, minimising the need for utilities relocation, for on and off-road running of the system. The research and development will provide demonstrator solutions in accordance with the project scope. The vehicle demonstrator will undergo extensive evaluation on test tracks to confirm its performance.</P>
